{"tid":1142854,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【區內新紀錄】六發展商財團近126億奪啟德地王 呎價逼2萬","createTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:28:27.000Z","uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8d51cf6800e4891901dd41954886d10daa83cd79","tid":1142854,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"【區內新紀錄】六發展商財團近126億奪啟德地王 呎價逼2萬 <br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2019年5月7日<br />\n<br />\n東九啟德跑道區再現百億地王，地政總署公布，啟德跑道區前排的第4C區2號住宅地，由會德豐（0020）、華懋、中國海外(0688)、恒地(0012)、新世界(0017)及帝國集團合組重量級財團，以125.9億元奪得地皮，每方呎樓面地價高見19636元，創啟德住宅地新高，亦較今年1月，新地（0016）以112.6億元、每方呎樓面地價17,360元投得的第4C區3號地皮高約13%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，上述地皮面積105,110方呎，可建樓面641,168方呎，位於啟德跑道區，毗鄰龍頭發展商新地今年1月以112.6億元、每方呎樓面地價17,360元投得的第4C區3號地皮，地皮同樣位於跑道區前排，可享全維港海景。"},{"pid":"f26c592c78c12cc814c18bd9242b112ddae97d3a","tid":1142854,"uid":93986,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"$30000呎指日可待"},{"pid":"b45e0e81320686497c2af2e49a5305d452a5fd75","tid":1142854,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"東九收地都2萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06d7a9dfce034bc818661628ea124efddc4341a","tid":1142854,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />升"},{"pid":"80da9b4360b95e1f92c149002aaf4563cf881e9d","tid":1142854,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14673b5820a7bc27279ea25aa21142feba3d9ec","tid":1142854,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" c